Are we looking at what @joshtpm calls a “shitload of obstruction?” TPM reporter Josh Kovensky joins our new podcast to discuss the top takeaways from the blockbuster Mueller report and how Congress is likely to act on it.

@joshtpm also shares how taking apart a Grady’s container is reminiscent of slaughtering an animal. (Tap the bio link to listen)

#MuellerReport #Mueller #JoshMarshallPodcast #Podcast

@joshtpm writes: “Michael Avenatti, playing a fairly weak hand, has managed to embarrass the President day after day for months. He outmaneuvers him. He’s inflicted immense damage on him.

You see something similar with Omarosa, even though she is a far, far less credible and creditable figure. She now seems likely to dribble out new tapes for days or weeks.

Avenatti and Manigault both have the adaptive skills of the Trump Era. They employ versions of his tactics. They have openings because of the scorched earth he has left in his wake.” #MichaelAvenatti #Avenatti #Omarosa #DonaldTrump #Trump
